        <mxCell id="d4RuPSLo96OGtzROQ47g-2" value="Запрашивается текущее состояние DINP, AINP, CNTINP, ALARMS_INFO. Для DINP данные копируются из буфера приема Rx (&amp;amp;fsm-&amp;gt;mb-&amp;gt;rxBuf[MODBUS_RX_DATA_OFF]) в буфер&amp;nbsp;&amp;amp;mod-&amp;gt;inp_data.discretes" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;" parent="1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="-790" y="-670" width="330" height="70" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="1H-obPz8-rYO6zvIR5Bk-1" value="&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;kbus_task&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;1&quot;&gt;kbus.c - (310)&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;" parent="1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="-870" y="-1450" width="200" height="50" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="1H-obPz8-rYO6zvIR5Bk-2" value="Вызывает&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;kbuscomm_process пока не прошли по всем шагам KBus.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;Шаг STATE_FINISHED сигнализирует kbus_task, что прошли по всем шагам state и можно перейти к следующему модулю.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px; text-align: center; background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;kbus_task вызывает&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px; text-align: center; background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;kbuscomm_start&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-size: 18px; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;вместо&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-size: 18px; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;kbuscomm_process.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;" parent="1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="-620" y="-1450" width="275" height="190" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="1H-obPz8-rYO6zvIR5Bk-3" value="&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;kbuscomm_start&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;1&quot;&gt;kbus_comm.c - (267)&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;" parent="1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="-870" y="-1257.5" width="200" height="50" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="1H-obPz8-rYO6zvIR5Bk-4" value="&lt;span style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;kbuscomm_start запускает опрос нового модуля с шага KBUSCOMM_STATE_DINP&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;" parent="1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="-620" y="-1247.5" width="275" height="70" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="1H-obPz8-rYO6zvIR5Bk-5" value="&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;kbuscomm_process&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;1&quot;&gt;kbus_comm.c - (288)&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;" parent="1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="-870" y="-1147.5" width="200" height="50" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="1H-obPz8-rYO6zvIR5Bk-6" value="&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;Продолжает опрос модуля, если шаг state KBus не последний.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;При этом всегда вызывает mb_process и если в mb_process достигли шага&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;STATE_READY, то происходит вызов функции&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;handle_ready,&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;" parent="1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="-620" y="-1147.5" width="275" height="167.5" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="1H-obPz8-rYO6zvIR5Bk-8" value="&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;kbuscomm_handle_ready&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;1&quot;&gt;kbus_comm.c - (217)&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;" parent="1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="-890" y="-960" width="220" height="50" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="1H-obPz8-rYO6zvIR5Bk-9" value="&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;, которая записывает значения DINP, AINP в&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;inp_data.discretes и&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-size: 18px; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;inp_data.analogs, переводя шаг&amp;nbsp; KBus или ничего не делает, а только переводит шаг&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;KBus.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;" parent="1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="-620" y="-970" width="275" height="130" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
      </root>
    </mxGraphModel>
